{"tid":1285484,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾維斯：巴西輸波全隊責任 阿根廷就美斯承擔","createTime":"2019-07-04T15:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T05:38:00.000Z","uid":34571,"like":11,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b3ea377778fbd9e767761124314eca7140e5de","tid":1285484,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"在昨天結束的美洲盃4強中，美斯率領的阿根廷被巴西隊淘汰出局。賽後巴西老將艾維斯（D.Alves）在接受採訪時，仍然不忘維護自己的好友美斯（L.Messi）。<br />\n<br />\n  艾維斯表示：「成為世界上最好的球員一定非常難，如果我們今天輸掉了比賽，那麼責任一定是每個人的，但在阿根廷，一切都是美斯的錯。我們整球隊都在發揮自己，而在阿根廷，只是美斯和少數幾個同伴。」<br />\n<br />\n  賽後美斯罕見炮轟了球證，他認為球證漏判了阿根廷2次12碼，對此艾維斯表示：「我同意美斯的看法，球證比我們還要緊張。」"},{"pid":"6b7b2a14e9730ba182ec3e7c425ef4a700993b51","tid":1285484,"uid":196924,"like":29,"dislike":6,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:05:26.000Z","msg":"贏嗰陣就話係美斯carry<br />\n輸嗰陣就唔可以話佢錯?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a02f81e7671d9fffa94f8a2346ab22b68440b93","tid":1285484,"uid":77805,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:02:30.000Z","msg":"幫美斯打曬飛機 似想返巴塞"},{"pid":"b77de0736d512bc76bcf7fd7e58a12cce0e5710c","tid":1285484,"uid":13281,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:09:07.000Z","msg":"只要美斯樂意既話就隨時可以入兩三球<br />\n但因為佢唔樂意搞到出局唔怪佢怪邊個呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3222dcacce4f171b810335010047173c5c85be86","tid":1285484,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:33:40.000Z","msg":"丹狗贏左講風涼話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac06e7203c286dd2ccc903bbcc953028e6352871","tid":1285484,"uid":56649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:35:33.000Z","msg":"果然真係豬隊友錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d4737adb53f61619f97a607b99d34062171a66","tid":1285484,"uid":15830,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:31:17.000Z","msg":"阿根廷輸波關美斯撚事？"},{"pid":"ac55581e997695a7dd977813fa9bbaff932d77b3","tid":1285484,"uid":53855,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T19:02:48.000Z","msg":"小花真係小花，輸波都仲有前巴塞拍檔幫佢辯解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba77180041801b4592b7271bcb8ba89baefc0772","tid":1285484,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T19:06:51.000Z","msg":"學野啦古天奴"},{"pid":"fe2904c27c2a1d8de6ab4a6ccce563981c1114ab","tid":1285484,"uid":33660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b7b2a14e9730ba182ec3e7c425ef4a700993b51","tid":1285484,"uid":196924,"like":29,"dislike":6,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:05:26.000Z","msg":"贏嗰陣就話係美斯carry<br />\n輸嗰陣就唔可以話佢錯?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:41:25.000Z","msg":"溫室小花要細心呵護"},{"pid":"7d84eefc936ef9bc975a42b6b50fe5495a9616c4","tid":1285484,"uid":232575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:38:00.000Z","msg":"好似由14年起，巴西輸波係因為無出尼馬（18年世界盃有出）。<br />\n<br />\n好似係尼馬負責多過集體負責"}]}